summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed from Kent Lumber Company, a corporation, to certain land in Sections Thirteen (13) and Twenty-four (24), Township Twenty-two (2) North of range Seven (7) East, W. M., and certain lands in Sections Eight (8) and Eighteen (18), Township Twenty-two (22) North of Range Eight (8) East, W. M., subject to certain reservations.
